Southern Union Co said it filed withthe Securities and Exchange Commission a registration statementcovering a 50 mln dlr offering of 10-year notes and asame-sized issue of 30-year debentures.    Proceeds will be used to redeem three outstanding debentureissues and repay two outstanding note issues.    The company named Goldman, Sachs and Co as sole manager ofthe note and debenture offerings. Reuter&#3;